(114, 3, '2022-02-17 20:04:46', '2022-02-17 20:04:46', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fireball was just a normal person.  When he was born his parent\'s named him that.  At the start he was really fast and when he got his powers it happened in a wildfire. Fireball is 10 years old.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Well, he was really nice to people before he got his powers like this time when he was 6.  He gave a baby a lollipop. And like this time when he was 7, he helped a person that was getting bullied. And like this time when he was 3. He saved a person from a fire. How did he figure out how to get in if the door was locked?  Probably the door just burnt down.  And like this time when he was 2, he stopped a robber from robbing a bank. And like this time when he was 9. he saved a person from falling out of a plane.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Well the fire helps people when its really dark and someone is going to kidnap them or murder them.  And his super speed makes tornados to destroy his enemies.  And this is his arch nemesis: Spike.  He plans on taking over the world and he kills people.  His powers are super strength, telekineses, and whoever he touches dies.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Check back to see our first book</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The Origin Story - Fireball', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-origin-story-fireball', '', '', '2022-02-17 20:15:42', '2022-02-17 20:15:42', '', 0, 'https://finneas.fuzzylojic.com/?p=114', 0, 'post', '', 0),
