(118, 3, '2022-02-17 20:22:28', '2022-02-17 20:22:28', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Fireball was just having a normal day, until Spike came and started floating houses and crushing people. And Fireball shot one of his fireballs at him. Spike floated a house over Fireball\'s head. Fireball moved.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Meanwhile, Spike\'s brother was making a wildfire. And Fireball\'s sister was using her water powers to put out the wildfire. and the wildfire went out. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Spike\'s brother is named Stone Heart.  His powers are can make earthquakes and can pick up any type of rock or ground, not like house ground.  Like earth ground. And he can make people blind for 10 minutes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fireball\'s sister is named Waterfall. Her powers are water powers and can make blind people see for one hour.  And she can teleport herself and other mammals, humans, and animals. And she can turn invisible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After the wildfire was put out. Spike and Stone Heart ran off to their secret lair. The lair looks like a giant spikey heart and it is made out of diamonds.  It is hiding inside of a mountain.  They are planning their next attack on the town and other towns. The name of the town they are attacking now is Skyerville.  Their plan to attacking Skyerville destroying all of the houses and kidnapping all of the people to make them work in the mines. Will they succeed?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Check back for the next book, Fireball Book 2 coming soon!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Fireball-Book One', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fireball-book-one', '', '', '2022-03-31 17:05:20', '2022-03-31 17:05:20', '', 0, 'https://finneas.fuzzylojic.com/?p=118', 