(182, 3, '2022-05-26 15:14:00', '2022-05-26 15:14:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It\'s been two weeks since Spike and Stoneheart attacked the city and Fireball has found a secret map in the basement of his house. Then he traveled through forests and mountains and even volcanoes and the north pole. Then he was there...at the secret underground base of Stoneheart and Spike.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Meanwhile, Spike\'s sister Abyss, and Fireball\'s secret brother were fighting because Abyss was trying to lift a small town with her super strength and flying so she could throw it at Fireball\'s secret brother. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">Fireball\'s secret brother\'s name is Blaze</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The next day Fireball was looking for his secret brother with the map because he thought that it would bring him to his secret brother. But it only led him to a clue and another map and that clue said \"Whoever enters, they will never come out\".  Fireball says \"As if!\"  And then he goes in.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fireball sees a trail that leads to two other trails. And a sign in the middle of it. The sign said \"One is trapped and the other is just a trail.\" </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The reader now gets to choose. Go left or right to see what happens.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You chose left:  You go left and then you fall in a pit of lava. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You are blind, you don\'t get to look.  Then is swaps 6 times.  Go left or right.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You go right: And you ended up at a dead end.  And then Fireball goes back. And then he looks down back to where the sign is and sees that a path opened up.  So he goes there and he sees a maze.  There is a map but it doesn\'t show the way.  It only shows what there is in the maze.  Fireball looks at it and he sees two things, there is a dragon and there is a lightning storm.  He goes the way that he see\'s the lightning storm and he finds instead of a lightning storm a sword.  It was just lying on the ground.  He picked it up and then he had the power to shoot lightning.  Now he has fire, super speed, and lightning powers...</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Find out next time on Fireball Book 3.  Coming Soon.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Fireball Book Two', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fireball-book-two-preview', '', '', '2022-06-25 18:49:29', '2022-06-25 18:49:29', '', 0, 'https://finneas.fuzzylojic.com/?p=182', 0, 'post', '', 0),
