(207, 3, '2022-06-23 16:52:32', '2022-06-23 16:52:32', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fireball is still looking for his long lost brother and he follows the map until...he finds a dungeon! He says, \"Uh this seems scary\".  He wants to walk away but he feels that the dungeon door closed.  SO he stays up there, in 5 minutes he walks down.  And when he walks down he finds fifteen cells.  He thinks that maybe Blaze, his long lost brother, was down there.  Pause - did anyone see the small words in the last book?  If you didn\'t then here\'s what it said: Fireball\'s secret brother is named Blaze.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>SO then once he was down there.  He looked and each cell was empty.  No one to be found.  Then he saw a hallway.  He went down it.  There were 20 more cells down there.  But then the same thing happened.  He looked in each cell and there was no one to be found.  Then he went down another hallway.  And there was 30 cells there.  And then he finally found someone.  He walked up to the cell.  The unknown person said, \"Are you one of the cops?\"  Then Fireball said, \"No.\"  Then the unknown person said one more thing, \"Then who are you?\"  Fireball said, \"My name is Fireball.\"  The unknown person gasped!  \"Fireball? Fireball, Fireball, Fireball...hmm? Is is really you? Brother?\"  Fireball said, \"Is your name Blaze?\"  The unknown person said, \"Yes!\" \"I finally found you!\" Fireball said. \"Let\'s get out of here!\"\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"We can\'t,\" said Blaze.  \"Why?\" said Fireball.  \"Because, my cell is locked with 6 layers of titanium\" Fireball says, \"I think I might be able to melt it.\"  Blaze replied, \"How, what\'s your powers?\"  \"Fire, super speed, and lightning,\" Fireball said.  Blaze replied, \"How did you get lightning???\" \"Well, I was in a maze and there was a lightning storm, and I found a lightning sword and it gave me this power of lightning.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Blaze said, \"Ok, so, it wasn\'t a lightning storm. It was just a lightning sword... And you got lightning powers from it?\" Fireball said, \"Yes. And then I came to find you.\" Then Blaze said, \"Where did you even find the lightning sword??\" \"You don\'t remember? I found it in a maze.\" replied Fireball.  \"I remember it a little bit,\" said Blaze. \"Just not enough to remember up to this point. Wait a minute! I\'m in a cell! Can you get me out of here?\" </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Then Fireball said, \"How did you get in this cell?\" \"I was captured six years ago.\" \"So you were two when you were captured??\" inquired Fireball. \"About to be three,\" said Blaze. \"Six people captured me.\" Fireball said, \"What were their names?\" \"I don\'t know,\" said Blaze. \"Now let\'s stop talking and GET ME OUT OF HERE!\" </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"OK, OK,\" said Fireball. \"I\'ll get you out of here, uhh, with that fork! To get the lock out.\" \"It\'s not that easy,\" said Blaze. \"Why not?\" said Fireball. \"Because. Don\'t you remember? This cage is made out of six layers of titanium.\" \"So what can I use to get you out?\" \"The only thing you can use is to get the steel chopper in what used to be a room for guards only.\" \"Where is it?\" \"Go down two more hallways, then go six, um, cells down, then you\'ll find a door that says, \'Guards Only\'.\" \"What if a guard gets me?\" said Fireball. Blaze responded, \"There isn\'t anyone else here.\" \"Why?\" said Fireball. \"Because, there was a big explosion two years ago. And I was left in my cell. The guards never got me out in time and I\'ve just been sitting here ever since<sup>1</sup>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"Ok, so I go two halls down, then I go six cells and then I\'ll see \'Guards Only\' sign on a door?\" \"Exactly,\" said Blaze. \"Ok, see you later or soon I should say,\" said Fireball. \"See ya,\" said Blaze. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Then Fireball went down two hallways then he went six cells then he found a door that said \'Guards O\'.\" Fireball said to himself, \"That\'s a pretty old sign.\" Fireball went in and saw ten different chainsaws and he thought that one of them might be the steel cutter that Blaze was talking about. So he went in, he looked if one of them would cut a piece of steel on the table. He went through five different ones before he finally found the steel cutter. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>He went back to Blaze. Then Fireball said, \"I have the steel cutter!\" Blaze was relieved saying, \"Now get me out of here!\" \"Ok,\" said Fireball, \"but you might have to back up.\" Then it happened. One second later, all of the six layers were gone. Blaze said, \"YES! I can finally get out of here. Thanks brother!\" Then they walked back to the door that had closed on Fireball earlier. With Blaze\'s help, they could burn the titanium filled wood.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Then they got through. They figured out something that everyone here reading this wouldn\'t have known (maybe). Blaze and Fireball could fly with their fire powers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks for reading! Read Fireball Book 4: The Family Find, coming soon. Bye! See you next book!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\"><sup>1</sup>Blaze had a secret stash of a lifetime supply of food and water.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Fireball Book 3: The Dungeon', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fireball-book-3-the-dungeon-a-preview', '', '', '2022-06-27 16:04:45', '2022-06-27 16:04:45', '', 0, 'https://finneas.fuzzylojic.com/?p=207', 0, 'post', '', 1),
