(217, 3, '2022-06-27 16:15:26', '2022-06-27 16:15:26', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Starting back on Fireball and Blaze.  They got out of the dungeon and they\'re heading back to the city.  Blaze said \"How much longer until we get back to city?\"  Fireball said \"We\'re almost there. Maybe one hour.\"  \"What is different there from the city since I was two?\" \" Not much.\" said Fireball. \"All that changed since you were two is a new jello store opened. And another bakery.\"  \" Wow, that\'s all that changed?\" said Blaze.  \"Yes. Almost there.  Five more minutes.  I can already see it\" said Fireball.  \"Me too ,\" said Blaze.  \"Here we are\", said Fireball.  Blaze said, \"Hey, let\'s go to your house.\"  \"Ok,\" said Fireball.  \"Well we\'re not that far from my house.  Just three blocks down and we\'ll be there.\"  \"Well let\'s go,\" said Blaze.   </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Three blocks later...\"Here we are.\" said Fireball.  \"WOW, THIS IS A BIG HOUSE!\" said Blaze.  \"I know,\" said Fireball.  \"Well let\'s go in.  And then I want to find the rest of our family.  At least our mom and dad.\"  Well, we\'re going to have to find another map or we just adventure and look and try to find our mom and dad,\" said Fireball.  \"Hey wait! I noticed that there was a piece of paper on your roof,\" said Blaze. \"REALLY!\" said Fireball.  \"Then let\'s go outside and get it! We might find our mom and dad with it!  And also it might be a map to them.  Let\'s go!\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fireball and Blaze started climbing up Fireball\'s house when they found the piece of paper they were talking about.  Fireball said, \"this is actually a map!\"  \"Ok, then let\'s get it.\" said Blaze.  \"Ok,\" said Fireball. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>shwoooooooooooooooooo</em>sh</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"Got it!\" said Fireball.  \"But can you help me up here!  I\'m going to get thrown away by the wind!\"  \"Ok!,\" said Blaze.  \"And I know, it\'s really windy! Has it always been this windy in town?\"  \"No,\" said Fireball.  \"It\'s only been this windy once.  This is the second time it\'s happened.  But it\'s much more dangerous when you are up on top of a house.  Good thing I have a spike on top of my house.  Because it makes it so I don\'t fall! Now help!  It\'s getting more windier by the minute!\" </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"Ok, I\'m going to use this rope I found in your house\" said Blaze.  \"Ok, what color is it?\" said Fireball.  \"It\'s red,\" said Blaze.  Don\'t use that one.  It is a really special one.  It\'s going to set everything on fire!\" said Fireball. \"Ok, I found another normal looking one\".  \"What color?\"  \"It\'s just a plain rope.\"  \"Ok, I guess you can use it\"  \"Ok, now give it to me and I will climb down with the map.\"  \"Ok,\" said Blaze.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Then Fireball climbed down.  But once they saw the map it headed back into the dungeon.  \"What does it say on it?\" said Blaze.  \"Here we go again.\" said Fireball.  \"Where?\" said Blaze.  Back into the dungeon we go.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Fireball Book 4 - The Family Find', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fireball-book-4-the-family-find', '', '', '2022-06-29 14:25:22', '2022-06-29 14:25:22', '', 0, 'https://finneas.fuzzylojic.com/?p=217', 0, 'post', '', 0),
