(231, 3, '2022-10-03 17:23:49', '2022-10-03 17:23:49', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Today they were starting to put up the decorations.  They had the cake and the presents ready.  They were almost done with the decorations until Fireball woke up.  They heard him and told him to stay in his room.  He almost opened the door when his parents, his brother, and his sister told him to keep the door closed.  And then they put the balloons through the hallway and then they told him that he could open the door.  He opened the door, he saw the balloons but he didn\'t see his parents, brother, or sister.  He went down the hall and before he could get to the living room they all jumped from behind the couch and said \"Happy Birthday!\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One hour later.... Fireball was ready to open his presents.  He opened one and he saw his favorite thing in there, he lost it when he was nine, his phone.  The next present he found was actually super cool, a PS-10.  The next present he opened was something that I have, a Nintendo Switch and a few games.  The next present he opened was funny, it was a box with another box in it.  And then another and then another and then another. And then finally he found something that he knew that he would never get again that wasn\'t physical a new SUPER POWER!!!  pause... Now he has four super powers!  Fire, super speed, lightening, and earth bending!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The next present he opened was super cool, it was an infinite balloon.  Do you want to know why it was so cool?  Because it was invincible and would it follow him at all times.  And it would attack anything...unpause.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Fireball was done opening presents for now.  They went outside to do some stuff.  Fireball knew that his fire could make him fly.  So he tried it out outside and it actually worked!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":254,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://finneas.fuzzylojic.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/fb-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-254\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">After he was done doing that, they left to go to the river where they found some unsuspecting people. Spike and Stone.  Before Spike and Stone saw them they hid behind a tree. or 5 trees to be exact.  Spike and Stone looked and they didn\'t see anyone except for, obviously, their dad.  Because he was the biggest one there so he couldn\'t fit behind a tree.  Then Spike and Stone came over there and then they all jumped out and were ready to fight.  But Spike and Stone just walked right by them. They didn\'t know why because Fireball, their dad and mom, were their arch nemesisisisisisis. But then once they all looked at each other, they didn\'t see the other four.  All they saw was air and ground and a few trees.  Then they noticed what they were touching that was on the trees was invisible goo. And they ran towards Spike and Stone.  And unexpectedly tackled Spike and Stone since they hated them.  Except FOR BLAZE.  But Blaze just stopped them all. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">When Spike and Stone got up, which actually they weren\'t even on the ground, because when they all tried to tackle Spike and Stone they just went through them.  And then they finally noticed that it wasn\'t invisible goo.  It was ghost goo.  It made them like a ghost but they weren\'t really ghosts.  Pause.... this is what they can\'t do from an actual ghost, they can\'t go through walls, they can\'t possess people, and they can\'t turn other people into a ghost because ghosts have ghost goo on them which turns other people into ghosts.  This is what they can do; they can go through people, no one can hear them, and they can\'t be seen.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>When the effect of the goo finally wore off it was already noon. So they went back home.  They started dinner and then they had a small and fun party at the house.  They ate dinner, had some delicious element cake which is actually really good, and then they ready to keep partying until they found something that flew through their window a day ago.  It was a treasure map. Pause.... they actually all have real people normal jobs instead of their super hero jobs.  And they did it all, I mean, they did those jobs out of the books. So you didn\'t get to see it...unpause.  Fireball said that they should go find what treasure there was. Spoiler alert; don\'t read this if you don\'t want to know a few things about the next book.  Here are the things; 1) you\'re actually going to get to read about them getting their real normal people jobs, 2) there gonna go on vacation cuz their boss told them that they should have some vacation time because they have been working too much and saving the world and all of that stuff, 3) they are going to follow the treasure map and it will lead to a different town.  They have to dig down all the way until there is starting to be cave dust everywhere, 4) the treasure is going to be a crystal.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-small-font-size\">The crystal costs millions of dollars</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Check back on this website to see the next Fireball Book 7; the Awesome Treasure.  See you later!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Fireball Book 6 _ The Epic Birthday#event theme', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fireball-book-6-_', '', '', '2022-10-18 18:33:51', '2022-10-18 18:33:51', '', 0, 'https://finneas.fuzzylojic.com/?p=231', 0, 'post', '', 2),
